Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.97,0:01:42.45,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur2}沉沒在拂曉之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.92,0:01:48.88,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur2}帶著偽造的臉龐 悄悄地靠近
